thread.title_full: Express Medical Supply reviewed by Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text: A positive note is that they carry a full range of medical supplies. On the negative side, shipping fees of almost $9.00 for two small, light items makes no sense. I let the order go through since I needed the gloves and face masks, but will never shop here again.
